  "quirks": "Momentum system: Store Momentum freezes and banks current velocity at no cost; Release Momentum spends 1 meter plus a stored charge to launch with it (optionally flipped) - this powers Ninja's signature burst movement and combo extensions. Sticky Bomb detonation is NOT a move: it is the 'Detonate' extra toggle ({explode: true} in turn extra data) usable alongside another action; manual detonation deals 80 (proration 3), automatic detonation 100 (proration 0). Substitution requires a live projectile (most recently created, within range). The shuriken states are internally named Fireball/AirFireball. Grappling Hook (state GrapplingHook, Special, air OK) exists in-game but is missing from this community table. Meter moves: Quick Slash 1 meter, Release Momentum 1 meter, Caltrops 3 meter. Always trust the runtime legal-move list from LegalMoveEnumerator over this table; frame data is community-sourced (YomiBot) and may drift from the current patch. ActionType follows the game enum (Movement/Attack/Special/Super/Defense); AirType is the state's usability enum (Grounded/Aerial/Both)."
}
